飞行侦察兵和危险地带模式、竞争地图和僚机地图、车间地图、Mac 和 Linux 支持，以及将武器交换到玩家屏幕左侧的功能。</p><p>在对缺失功能列表的回应中，有人将其与<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/overwatch-2"><em>《守望先锋 2》</em></a>的发布进行了<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/GlobalOffensive/comments/16uc19t/comment/k2xz673/?utm_source=reddit&amp;utm_medium=web2x&amp;context=3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">比较</a>，并且粉丝普遍认为原版<em>《守望先锋》</em>更优秀。</p><p>还有针对<em>《反恐精英 2</em> 》反作弊系统的投诉，但该游戏最近才发布，有关非法行为的信息可能仍在收集和分析中。</p><p>关于这个话题，Valve 表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-will-penalise-players-for-associating-with-cheaters-3506446">与游戏中的作弊者“交往”</a>将足以受到惩罚，例如失去个人资料排名和 CS 评级。 </p><figure id="attachment_3507748" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3507748" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3507748" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-missing-features-from-global-offensive-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-missing-features-from-global-offensive-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-missing-features-from-global-offensive-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-missing-features-from-global-offensive-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-missing-features-from-global-offensive-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-missing-features-from-global-offensive-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-missing-features-from-global-offensive-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3507748" class="wp-caption-text"> 《反恐精英 2》来源：Valve</figcaption></figure><p>虽然开发者尚未发布有关这些功能的公告，但希望它们能够在未来几个月内以某种形式的更新来支持游戏的粉丝。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/mortal-kombat-1">《